Class Cons

Direct Known Subclasses:
Nil
public class Cons
extends Object

A Scheme pair. car and cdr are slots, some other list access functions (ie, cadr) are implemented as methods. Methods starting with k (ie, kdr and kadr) perform an access and cast their result to another Cons. The list methods are convenient for creating lists from within Java code.
